articles.title: Consumer Price Index climbs 3.6% YoY in December, as expected - FXStreet
articles.description: Australia’s Consumer Price Index (CPI) climbed by 3.6% year-over-year (YoY) in December, following a 3.5% increase (revised from 3.4%) reported in the previous reading, the latest data published by the Australian Bureau of Statistics (ABS) showed on Wednesday.
